# Nextcloud Homelab Documentation

## Goal

Replace Google Photos and Google Drive with a self-hosted alternative running on a repurposed laptop. Full control over personal files and photos, no third-party cloud dependency.

---

## Hardware

| Component | Details |
|---|---|
| Primary Server | Asus Vivobook S15 S530U (2018) — Intel Core i5-8250U, 8GB RAM |
| Storage | WD Blue 1TB 2.5" SATA HDD (9mm), ~$45–60 |
| Test Machine | Old Acer Laptop |
| Installation Media | USB Flash Drive |
| OS | Ubuntu Server 22.04 LTS |
| Tools | Balena Etcher |

---

## Software Stack

| Layer | Software |
|---|---|
| OS | Ubuntu Server 22.04 LTS |
| Web Server | Apache 2.4.52 |
| Database | MySQL |
| PHP | 8.2 |
| App | Nextcloud (latest) |

